{"tid":800851,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"異國廚師一致偏愛　香港名物XO醬","createTime":"2018-08-31T07:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T10:53:14.000Z","uid":160973,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"db3dc54ec2f4f32e39be69bf5d2b996ae880f77c","tid":800851,"uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T07:48:25.000Z","msg":"因着東西文化差異，人們的飲食習慣自然不同。最典型的例子，就是我們常吃的皮蛋，經過數月的醃製，變成灰綠色，松花皮蛋更被奉為雋品，可惜「甲之蜜糖，乙之砒霜」，外國人更將之列為「全球最噁心的食物」之一。<br />\n<br />\n「每種食物都應該反映當地風土與DNA，而非入口的味道。」XO醬印證廚師Max Levy的這種看法。<br />\n<br />\n有趣的是，香港的XO醬，罕有地得到不少異國廚師青睞，讚口不絕。原因之一，是XO醬顛覆了法國料理的用醬傳統，法式醬汁總是慢火熬製、濃縮，收至不見一滴油脂。中式的卻來得豪邁熱情，XO醬裏盡是油，卻絲毫不覺膩滯。個性鮮明的XO醬，就似把香港的海味街收進其中，充分顯出了粵菜的醬汁風格，成為最有特色的香港醬料。<br />\n<br />\n直到現在，中外廚師都喜歡自製XO醬，因為它是一種體現廚師功力的手工製作，由選定十多種材料與比例，到炒製的力度，都可以辨出廚藝高下。Okra的主廚Max Levy從十二年前開始便自製XO醬，「當時市面只有李錦記一種XO醬，幾乎每間餐廳都會自製，但那些味道較接近辣椒醬。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2PoI9RD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PoI9RD&d=0%2F%2Bsm2iTreXJo34rCNGgVv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=4c16365f\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2PoI9RD</a>"},{"pid":"f149bf994d509f7179362f09204c98ba8f854ee7","tid":800851,"uid":105715,"like":9,"dislike":9,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T07:51:35.000Z","msg":"XO醬個名來源都好有香港人精神<br />\n充大頭鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a9d6a0b439d8b50ae878baefc315ba7a46b2011","tid":800851,"uid":31920,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:02:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>XO醬個名來源都好有香港人精神<br />\n充大頭鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都有得踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加你人工<br />\n$0.55"},{"pid":"5a36c22fcca0e979534410da44ec80d730df1a45","tid":800851,"uid":159083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:04:57.000Z","msg":"好鍾意食入面果啲蝦米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a78f5e48b345771e7454a9de52d67adaba2c68ba","tid":800851,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5a36c22fcca0e979534410da44ec80d730df1a45","tid":800851,"uid":159083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:04:57.000Z","msg":"好鍾意食入面果啲蝦米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:09:48.000Z","msg":"瑤柱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c3535194c8dd039d50ca2835d08bf1af24719f","tid":800851,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:11:40.000Z","msg":"食點心時落d 真係無得輸"},{"pid":"39f89511624504fffae3854ce8235e7109267f95","tid":800851,"uid":60668,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:40:28.000Z","msg":"「桌子上放了什麼醬料，都有意思的。像香港人以前吃餃子，會用喼汁，現在大家都用鎮江醋。」"},{"pid":"865ad919965046af3a22d1c460e0f2139410b30a","tid":800851,"uid":80980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:43:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>XO醬個名來源都好有香港人精神<br />\n充大頭鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都有得踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加你人工<br />\n$0.55</blockquote><br />\n企係高地踩港就係清高啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好有型好叻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff82f38cc7969ef765df55390e6a0cd80754ebb","tid":800851,"uid":48060,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f149bf994d509f7179362f09204c98ba8f854ee7","tid":800851,"uid":105715,"like":9,"disli